litics in America and raises valuable questions about the future of the American legal system.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAdversary system (Law)xUnited States. 0aDroit et politiquexUnited StatesxUSA. 0aJustice pénalexAdministrationxÉtats-Unis. 0aJustice, Administration ofxUnited States. 0aLawxPolitical aspects. 0aSystème accusatoire (Droit)xÉtats-Unis. 7aLAW / Comparative.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z978311044221240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674039278423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674039278/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK